    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276690/extras/aab6c209e95bbd457ec8590c02702bde.poster.avif?t=1760128442\" width=780 height=458 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276690/extras/aab6c209e95bbd457ec8590c02702bde.webm?t=1760128442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276690/extras/aab6c209e95bbd457ec8590c02702bde.mp4?t=1760128442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Trash Dungeon</strong> is an action-packed dungeon roguelike where you play as a rabid raccoon stealing trash and treasure in a trash dungeon.<br><br><strong>GAMEPLAY:</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276690/extras/c33b730ffe981a686118f5a9fe16fe42.poster.avif?t=1760128442\" width=780 height=694 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276690/extras/c33b730ffe981a686118f5a9fe16fe42.webm?t=1760128442\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3276690/extras/c33b730ffe981a686118f5a9fe16fe42.mp4?t=1760128442\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You are Mike, a raccoon with a ski-mask and a gun - and you have rabies. You must keep killing to stay alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep killing enemies and collect trash to rack up your combo. Collect treasures that give you crazy perks, which get stronger the higher your combo gets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, make sure you're collecting enough trash, or the Trash God will smite you before you get to the next level.</p>",
